column2: SELECT   m.specz_id,   m.specz_ra,      m.specz_dec,   (m.specz_redshift - f.z)/m.specz_redshift AS z_distance,   n.objid,    n.distance,   f.z,    f.zErr,    f.specobjid,   f.petroMag_g - f.petroMag_i AS gminusi,   gsl.h_alpha_eqw,   gsl.h_alpha_eqw_err,   gsl.h_beta_eqw,   gsl.h_beta_eqw_err   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.specz_ra, m.specz_dec, #) AS n    JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS f ON n.objid=f.objid    JOIN GalSpecLine as gsl on f.SpecObjID = gsl.SpecObjID
